description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 10, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 10, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Leverage for East, 5 for South, and Box for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70101-76544-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [10 Votes, Common]
